data.description: Welcome to Our Lovely Colonial Scranton Home!Property Features 3 Bedrooms and 2 Full Bathrooms with an Unfinished Basement. 1 Car garage and plenty of side and front yard space for BBQ Gardening and Outdoor Fun. The home is located at the end of a quiet block and offers plenty of street parking for guests.Home features a Front and Side Entrance with Mudroom/Den. Renovated Bathrooms!Brand New Roof!This Freshly Painted Home Can be used as a 4 Bedroom Railroad Style or a 3 Bedroom Suite.Unfinished Basement Contains A New Boiler and Water Heater.2 year old Roof!All practical upgrades that will make your move in a breeze!Traveling Home will be Very Convenient and Direct coming off the 11 Highway!Easiest Commute Home!5 minutes to Viewmont Mall and other popular Scranton Shopping and Necessities.See it Now! Won't Last!
